div.p:
Measures for helping and assisting the 

Political Progress,

Economic Progress, and

Social Progress of the Korean people;

Development of Democratic Self-Government of the Korean people;

Establishment of National Independence of Korea.

list.item:
The Koreans will need initial help, guidance, training in organization and
                        orderly procedures, and supervision backed by
                            authority if they are to get a good start for independence;

The Korean people will most likely become reconciled to a trusteeship when
                        they see the extent of authority enjoyed by the Provisional Government under
                        it and, presumably, the unobtrusiveness of the trusteeship agency;
